But he fell head first into the
spring.
"O, these heavy kids!" he cried.
They made me fall into the water.
Help me out! Help! help!"

90
XIX
Just then Mother Goat came
along.
"Help me out! Help me out!"
cried the wolf.
"O no," said the goat.
"I will not help you out.

